OL,3,CInside Britain's Asylum Crisis -
OL,4,CTonight
OL,6,FAnd as thousands of people fleeing
OL,7,Fpoverty and conflict continue to
OL,8,Farrive on Britain's shores, it's left
OL,9,Fmany like Lee feeling that asylum
OL,10,Fseekers are being given preferential
OL,11,Ftreatment including getting what's
OL,12,Fcalled a HC2 certificate which allows
OL,13,Fthem to receive NHS treatment
OL,14,Fincluding free prescriptions, dental
OL,15,Fcare and vouchers for glasses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
