OL,6,F"They've just jumped the queue,
OL,7,Fhaven't they? They they're they're.
OL,8,FThey're in, you know, they're getting
OL,9,Ftheir free medical health and, you
OL,10,Fknow, dental treatment, I have to ring
OL,11,Fup the you know, the local doctors
OL,12,Fand, and get an appointment, and I'm
OL,13,Flucky if I can get like within 3
OL,14,Fweeks." - Lee
OL,16,FWhilst they are usually given NHS
OL,17,Faccess, asylum seekers do not get
OL,18,Fpriority over other NHS users.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
