OL,3,CInside Britain's Asylum Crisis -
OL,4,CTonight
OL,6,FAs of June 2025, there were around
OL,7,Fthirty two thousand asylum seekers
OL,8,Fliving in hotels, In Blackpool, famous
OL,9,Ffor its seaside holidays, there has
OL,10,Fseen a significant increase in asylum
OL,11,Fseekers staying in hotel accommodation
OL,12,Fthere. It was here we met Sam who told
OL,13,FTonight that she quit her job as a
OL,14,FHousing Officer at the Metropole
OL,15,Fbecause she said she couldn't bear to
OL,16,Fsee people living with raw sewage and
OL,17,Frats running through the accommodation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
