OL,3,CInside Britain's Asylum Crisis -
OL,4,CTonight
OL,6,FWe also discovered that for some, life
OL,7,Finside the hotels can be even worse
OL,8,Fthan the conditions. We spoke to Sarah
OL,9,F( not her real name) who fled her
OL,10,Fcountry due to domestic abuse and
OL,11,Freligious persecution, but then found
OL,12,Fherself trapped in a hotel. She was to
OL,13,Fscared to go outside because of
OL,14,Fprotests but to scared to stay inside
OL,15,Fbecause of the sexual harassment she
OL,16,Ffaced from a British member of staff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
