OL,6,FMany live in houses of multiple
OL,7,Foccupancy or HMO;s as they are often
OL,8,Fcalled but in Portsmouth this has also
OL,9,Fcaused outrage after it emerged 55
OL,10,FHMO's were operating in the city
OL,11,Fwithout the council's knowledge. It
OL,12,Fprompted local residents Jack and Curt
OL,13,Fto take action. They covered their
OL,14,Ffaces with masks to avoid backlash
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
