OL,6,FOther options include the use of
OL,7,Fformer army barracks like Napier in
OL,8,FKent which is one of two former bases
OL,9,Fbeing used to house asylum seekers. It
OL,10,Fwas due to close but it;s believed the
OL,11,Fgovernment are considering extending
OL,12,Fits use despite The High Court ruling
OL,13,Fit was overcrowded and filthy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
