OL,3,CInside Britain's Asylum Crisis -
OL,4,CTonight
OL,6,FWhile protesters shout on the streets,
OL,7,Fpolitical parties shout from the
OL,8,Frooftops about how they will be the
OL,9,Fones to save Britain from its
OL,10,Fdeepening immigration crisis. It's
OL,11,Fclear there is no quick fix. But what
OL,12,Fis clear is that there is likely to be
OL,13,Fmore flags and fury on Britain's
OL,14,Fstreets.
OL,16,FYou can watch the Tonight programme
OL,17,F'Inside Britain's Asylum Crisis" on
OL,18,FThursday, 25th September at 8.30PM, on
OL,19,FITV1 and ITVX.
